snippet.title: Snacko 🌱 Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now in Early Access! Try the FREE demo on Steam
✨https://store.steampowered.com/app/1125510/Snacko

Set out for a new life away from the city to rebuild a town from scratch. Decorate, collect, produce, and befriend in this cat-ivating life sim! 

Thank you for having us in your first ever pre-show, OTK Expo 💖

-------------------------------------------------
Thank you to the players who provided their save files so I could get these beautiful shots~
cloud, Farren, Luna, AirysPaw
